summary:
üìçAfter completing my exchange semester at FHWien der WKW, I am now onto the next adventure - a logistics internship at OMV. 

üë©‚ÄçüíºI am an ambitious, resourceful, and studious third-year student of international business. I am a critical thinker, problem-solver, and multitasker, with diverse experience including digital marketing (copywriting, CRM), primary logistics, entrepreneurship, and teaching. My favorite things are strategizing and presenting. 

üåç Living in 5 countries (the USA, Malta, Bulgaria, Austria, and the Netherlands) has contributed to my cultural awareness. I can confidently say I thrive in an international community.
